==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Observation deck
<hw>Ob`ser*va"tion deck</hw>. <def>A room or platform at a high point in
a tall building with a broad view of the surrounding area. It is often
an outdoor platform, but is sometimes indoors in a room with large
windows to accommodate viewing.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Observation post</ent>⟦br⟧
